	<h1 class="title">恒大战巴萨，郑智脚上穿的是一双国产战靴</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/26306/small/26306.jpg?1455710291" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">宣海伦 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-16 08:12:21 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19160/medium/19160.jpg?1450196617" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


